dc_description_s: This point shapefile contains the locations of warehouses in Kenya for 2011. Data were acquired from the National Cereals and Produce Board (NCPB) in Kenya.This layer is intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
dc_publisher_s: United Nations. Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs
dc_creator_sm: Kenya. National Cereals and Produce Board
